(265, 146, 26, 0, 9, 0, 70, 0, 0, 0, 'Nov 20, 2011, Guwahati\n\nSir,\n\nWe, the people of Guwahati have seen so much of changes in our city in the last 20 years that it has now become quite difficult for us to recognize it. We find tall buildings being constructed everywhere, increasing number of flyovers here and there, increasing number of shopping malls, growing number of outlets for branded clothes, etc. People in the city nowadays are broadening their mindsets and have started changing according to the need of the present society. But, some things in the city have never changed and those have turned into serious issues for the people. One such burning issue is the problem of garbage disposal in the city.\n\nThere is lack of dustbins, sanitation facilities for years. As an alert citizen, we are reporting this issue for several years but still no proper action is taken from the government.\n\nPlease take some immediate action to save our city.\n\nPriyanka Sengupta', '2016-01-29 12:41:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 26.1445, 91.7362, 'C', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 0, '2016-02-03 11:42:55', '0', 'Garbage problems in Guwahati', 'Guwahati', NULL),
