(1, 2, ' Indian National Congress', 'ENG', '<div>According to the report, the Congress had planned to organise a public meeting at Talkatora sta', 'The Congress may havehad grand plans to celebrate the 124th birth anniversary of Bharat Ratna Babasaheb Ambedkar today, but the continuing sabbatical of Congress vice president Rahul Gandhi has reportedly forced the party to cancel a megaevent and settle for alow-key function instead.The party has now reportedly decided to launch its nationwide year-long celebrations at an event in Madhya Pradesh next month, which is expected to be attended by Rahul, according to thisIndian Expressreport.', '1431695500-cmgallery.jpg', 'Image', 1, '2015-05-26 15:28:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(2, 2, 'Sonia Gandhi speech', 'ENG', 'Rahul Gandhi takes the sole responsibility for the failure of Congress&nbsp;', '<div>Rahul Gandhi and Sonia Gandhi congratulated the new BJP Government. While speaking to media Rahul said that Congress party has done pretty badly in this elections. \"we believe that winning and losing are part of elections, we will put our effort to raise peoples issues as opposition and we congratulate the newly formed Telangana.\"said Sonia Gandhi.</div><div><br></div>', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p0l4w81jQvU', 'Youtube URL', 1, '2015-05-20 14:19:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(3, 8, 'Indira Nagar New Bus Stop', 'ENG', '<div>A new bus stop has been constructed on Indira Nagar.</div>', '<div>A new bus stop has been constructed on Indira Nagar &nbsp;for easy commuting. This location always needed a proper bus stop and we have made that happen now.</div><div><br></div>', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PiMM6CNA0j8', 'Youtube URL', 1, '2015-09-11 13:09:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(5, 8, 'Road development', 'ENG', '<div>The concrete road construction has been completed.</div>', '<div>The concrete road construction has been completed near MAHILA MAHAVIDYALAYA at AMINABAD,&nbsp;</div>', '1435139490-cmgallery.jpg', 'Image', 1, '2015-06-24 09:51:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(6, 8, 'Park development', 'ENG', 'Development of new parks would not only enhance the entire look of our ward.', 'Development of new parks would not only enhance the entire look of our ward but it would also add good health and fun outdoor activities for children.', '1436629737-cmgallery.jpeg', 'Image', 1, '2015-07-11 15:48:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7, 13, 'Launch pad for MIHAN', 'ENG', 'Launch pad for MIHAN at Nagpur City<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>', 'The project which has the potential of changing the fate of the entire Vidarbha region unfortunately was a victim of political apathy in the past few years. Shri Gadkari, who has been an advocate of the same since the very beginning, immediately took up the issue with the State and the Central governments to get the necessary sanctions. He also now heads a monitoring committee for the same project. The project which was earlier lying on the death bed has now got a new lease of life and is ready to take off.', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PiMM6CNA0j8', 'Youtube URL', 0, '2015-09-11 13:20:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8, 13, 'Propelling the Nagpur Metro Rail project', 'ENG', '<div>Propelling the Nagpur Metro Rail project</div><div><br></div>', '<div><br></div><div>A project that will change the face of the city, was under consideration of MoUD for past two years. Shri Gadkari followed up and got it approved from the cabinet and the ministry within two months. The foundation stone of the project was laid by Hon. PM Shri Narendra Modiji on 21st August 2014 and the work for the same has started with an unmatched speed.</div>', '1441797645-cmgallery.jpg', 'Image', 1, '2015-09-11 13:00:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
