(12, 26, 'ENG', 'Development of rural infrastructure, employment generation, promotion of small scale industries is the next thrust areas for the Government.', '2016-01-27 13:00:46'),
(13, 26, 'ENG', 'For the last fifteen years, I have taken up many developmental activities in Titabor. But I would say we have more to do in the field of education, employment, road and communication, agriculture. I want to complete the rest of the work and expedite development', '2016-03-18 13:12:09'),
(14, 26, 'ENG', 'Most of the people in Titabor are of the age of my son, cousin, daughter & grandson. I treat them as my own family', '2016-03-19 05:43:29'),
