(17, 26, 'ENG', 'In our next term, we will stress more on job creation. No other state has matched number of jobs created in ‪Assam‬. ', '2016-03-25 05:51:53'),
(18, 26, 'ENG', 'My birth and childhood in tea gardens and villages here have given me an understanding of the pain and problems of the rural areas.', '2016-03-27 06:33:31'),
