(23, 26, 'ENG', 'Anyone in the tea gardens does not possess a house will be given Pukka houses.', '2016-03-31 07:48:23'),
(27, 30, 'ENG', 'Committed to the upliftment of the poor and tribal people!', '2016-05-07 05:27:55'),
(28, 31, 'ENG', 'Men are not the creature of circumstances,\r\nCircumstances are the creatures of men.', '2016-04-02 06:51:43'),
(29, 26, 'ENG', 'We have fought the language movement to safeguard the interest of both Assamese and Bengali community.', '2016-04-06 05:51:53'),
(30, 26, 'ENG', 'We want to be in power to help the poor, to help the youth and bring more development in the state.', '2016-04-07 10:21:18'),
(31, 26, 'ENG', 'People will not vote by watching TV but they will vote by watching our work.', '2016-04-08 16:21:36'),
(33, 26, 'ENG', 'May this Bohag Bihu brings peace and prosperity in the lives of the people of Assam. Happy Bohag Bihu! ', '2016-04-13 05:48:42'),
(34, 26, 'ENG', 'A positive thought in the morning can make your whole day positive.', '2016-04-19 11:00:54'),
(35, 26, 'ENG', 'I have directed the Chief Secretary and Supply department to form a task force to monitor and control inflation.', '2016-05-07 07:31:06'),
(36, 26, 'ENG', 'We have to stress upon education in such a way that it provides economic development later.', '2016-05-08 17:11:49'),
(37, 26, 'ENG', 'The true meaning of life is discovered when you forward your hand to those who need it .', '2016-05-09 12:36:03'),
