(23, 16, 'ENG', 'Students and schools make good civic responsibility – Brijmohan', 'Raipur', 'Chhattisgarh', 'Raipur', '492001', 'If the Country has to succeed further we need to provide quality education  Currently standing academic traditions will benefit neither country nor the society Currently standing academic traditions will benefit neither country nor the society . Because the purpose of education today seems to be to get a job for only the best package, while being a good citizen first objective should be to contribute to the development of the country .', 'http://brijmohanagrawal.in/news-view/', 21.233, 81.6583, '2015-08-23 12:56:00', '2015-08-23 12:57:00', '1442215668-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2015-09-14 10:45:50'),
