(47, 26, 'ENG', 'Shri Tarun Gogoi filing nomination from Titabor', 'Titabor', 'Assam', 'Jorhat', '785630', 'Chief Minister Tarun Gogoi filed his nomination from his home constituency, Titabor today.  Addressing to a mass of supporters at the rally, Shri Tarun Gogoi asserted that he would continue to strive for excellence in the State.\r\n \'\'My victory depends on the love & blessings of the people of Titabor who have made us victorious in the previous 3 terms.\r\nI have always had immense faith in my party workers, we will win again this time & this will be the victory of the people of Titabor.\" CM quoted.', NULL, 26.5881, 94.1872, '2016-03-18 18:54:00', '2016-03-18 18:54:00', '1458307651-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-03-26 11:26:40'),
(51, 26, 'ENG', 'Launch of Election Manifesto ', 'Rajiv Bhavan', 'Assam', 'Guwahati', '781005', 'Shri Tarun Gogoi launched the Election ‎Manifesto‬ yesterday on the auspicious day of ‪Holi‬.\r\n \'\'In our next term, we will stress more on job creation. No other state has matched number of jobs created. ‪\r\nWe will give unemployment allowances of Rs 1000 each to most needy & set up innovation centres with venture capital of Rs 5500 cr. We will\r\nhold pre-selection tests for Paramilitary, Air Force, Navy, Railways & other sectors & also provide coaching centers for them. We will ensure registration of the unemployed youths of every district to train & counsel them. Opening of community kitchen for each village & adding breakfast along with the scheme of Mid-day meals will be some of our new initiatives.\'\' CM quoted', NULL, 26.1573, 91.7953, '2016-03-24 17:00:00', '2016-03-24 18:00:00', '1458884073-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-03-28 11:04:13'),
