(55, 26, 'ENG', 'Shri Tarun Gogoi in Borholla addressing the mass', 'Borholla', 'Assam', 'Jorhat', '785631', 'Shri Tarun Goigoi arrived in Borholla some time ago to meet the people over there.\r\n\r\n\"Today I have come to this rural area and want to thank you all for my victory for the last three terms. My birth and childhood in Tea gardens and villages here have given me an understanding of the pain and problems of the rural areas\" Mr. Gogoi quoted.\r\n\r\nMr Gogoi further added \"I might be old but I have the strength to work for the state. We are stressing on rural development and for that we will take initiative to set up small scale industries.Our victory is obvious\"', NULL, 26.4507, 94.1539, '2016-03-27 11:30:00', '2016-03-27 00:00:00', '1459062488-em.png', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-03-28 08:56:00'),
