(61, 26, 'ENG', 'A myriad of supporters at the Diphu rally', 'Diphu', 'Assam', 'East Karbi Anglong', '782460	', 'Men, women & a group of youth thronging at the Diphu rally to listen to the speech of Shri Tarun Gogoi. The people are very hopeful that this time also Shri Tarun will stand victorious in the upcoming assembly election.\r\n\r\nMr. Gogoi quoted addressing the crowd, \'\' We are for the development of every community and religion and with the same objective of development we have formed development council. We want development of Karbi Anglong, North Cachar and people will vote for us.\"\r\n\r\nMr. Gogoi further added, \" Unemployment is a crucial issue in Karbi Anglong and we will bring special schemes to solve this problem. We will set up industries to solve unemployment here and special package will be given to the people of Karbi Anglong.\"', NULL, 25.8465, 93.4299, '2016-03-29 12:30:00', '2016-03-29 13:30:00', '1459237145-em.png', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-03-30 08:18:45'),
