(69, 26, 'ENG', 'Public eagerly waiting for Shri Tarun Gogoi at Bokakhat', 'Rajabari', 'Assam', 'Golaghat', '785612', 'Public eagerly waiting for Shri Tarun Gogoi at the Bokakhat Rally', NULL, 26.3185, 94.0907, '2016-04-01 12:28:00', '2016-04-01 12:28:00', '1459493950-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-01 09:08:41'),
(70, 26, 'ENG', 'Bokakhat welcoming Shri Tarun Gogoi', 'Rajabari', 'Assam', 'Golaghat', '785612', 'The eagerly awaited crowd at Bokakhat wholeheartedly welcomed Shri Tarun Gogoi and listened to his profound speech with full interest.\r\n\r\n', NULL, 26.3185, 94.0907, '2016-04-01 14:00:00', '2016-04-01 15:00:00', '1459501141-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-02 07:22:41'),
(71, 26, 'ENG', 'Shri Tarun Gogoi attending a press meet in Jorhat ', 'Jorhat', 'Assam', 'Jorhat', '785112', 'Attending the press meet in Teok of Jorhat district, Shri Gogoi added, \" I have been taking active part in language movement, refinery and state re-organisation movement and I have started my political career from Jorhat and so I am organising this press meet in Jorhat which is the last one in my third tenure. I have fulfilled all the promises but certainly I have been successful in restoring peace. People are now not afraid of going out of the house. People gets killed in insurgency even today but there is no secret killings.\r\n\r\nShri Gogoi further added, \" Medical colleges are six in the state and three of these have been established during my government. Earlier Engineering colleges were only 2 and seats were 510. Now there are 17 Eng colleges and seats are 4010.\"', NULL, 26.73, 94.175, '2016-04-02 11:30:00', '2016-04-02 12:00:00', '1459579125-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-04 06:14:57'),
(72, 26, 'ENG', 'People of Teok are excited to meet Mr. Gogoi', 'Teok', 'Assam', 'Jorhat', '785112', 'Eagerly waiting crowd of Teok cheered for Shri Tarun Gogoi as he joins the rally and address their issues.\r\n\r\n', NULL, 26.8337, 94.4285, '2016-04-02 14:04:00', '2016-04-02 15:04:00', '1459589750-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-04 06:53:24'),
(73, 26, 'ENG', 'Dihing witnessed a mass of supporters at the rally', 'Dihing', 'Assam', 'Tinsukia', '786125', 'Dihing witnessed a huge gathering at the rally. This ensured that Shri Gogoi\'s supporters are with him and they want to see him stand victorious as a Chief Minister of Assam in his 4th term.\r\n\r\nVisit Gallery for more images.', NULL, 27.2849, 95.6693, '2016-04-03 12:30:00', '2016-04-03 13:30:00', '1459673629-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-04 07:01:04'),
(74, 26, 'ENG', 'Kaliabor being flooded with Shri Gogoi\'s supporters', 'Kaliabor', 'Assam', 'Nagaon', '782137', 'With people flooding the venue of the rally in Kaliabor of Nagaon district and cheering for their favourite man, Shri Tarun Gogoi is confident that people of Assam love him, trust him and they want to see him victorious in the assembly election. A very thoughtful statement quoted by Mr. Gogoi during his speech, \"My politics is to help and assist the poor people. We will continue working for them and also safeguard all religions.\" ', NULL, 26.5384, 92.9288, '2016-04-03 15:00:00', '2016-04-03 16:00:00', '1459684647-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-04 06:57:33'),
(75, 26, 'ENG', 'Meeting the people of Abhayapuri', 'Abhayapuri', 'Assam', 'Bongaingaon', '783384', 'Feeling overwhelmed with joy after today\'s 1st phase of election, Shri Gogoi addressed the people of Abhayapuri at the rally.\r\n\r\n\'Today, the huge response we got in the first phase of polls shows we will win by a huge margin.\' Shri Gogoi added.', NULL, 26.3589, 90.6485, '2016-04-04 15:00:00', '2016-04-04 16:00:00', '1459769274-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-04 13:02:56'),
(76, 26, 'ENG', 'Shri Gogoi supporting his new party candidate', 'West Guwahati', 'Assam', 'Guwahati', '781013', 'Shri Gogoi addressed a mass of crowd yesterday and also showed his support to the new candidate Juri Sharma Bordoloi of west Guwahati constituency.\r\n\r\nSpeaking in the interest of her, Gogoi said, \'We do not need MLAs who only sleeps and does not work. We need to vote for active MLAs.\'\r\n\r\nHe further added,\"We have fought the language movement to safeguard the interest of both Assamese and Bengali community and will continue to so.\'', NULL, 26.1504, 91.6518, '2016-04-05 18:00:00', '2016-04-05 19:00:00', '1459919138-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-07 12:01:56'),
(77, 26, 'ENG', 'Shri Tarun Gogoi with Shri Manmohan Singh at Chandrmari', 'Chandmari', 'Assam', 'Guwahati', '781003', 'The rally at Chandmari today drew a huge crowd of people flocking the venue to listen to the profound speech of the Chief Minister of Assam and Ex- Prime Minister of India.  Visit Gallery for more images.', NULL, 26.189, 91.7729, '2016-04-06 18:00:00', '2016-04-06 19:00:00', '1459962030-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-08 12:36:07'),
(78, 26, 'ENG', 'Mrs. Sonia Gandhi and Mr. Tarun Gogoi at Jagiroad', 'Jhargaon Jagiroad', 'Assam', 'Morigaon', '782410', 'Talking to a huge crowd of supporters present at the rally in Jagiroad, Shri Tarun Gogoi, and Mrs. Sonia Gandhi made an assurance that their party would continue to bring more progression in the district and overall state by being a friend to the poor people, helping the youth and women of the state. ', NULL, 26.1308, 92.2138, '2016-04-07 14:00:00', '2016-04-07 15:00:00', '1460026049-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-08 05:46:27'),
(79, 26, 'ENG', 'Panbazaar and Fancy Bazaar witnessed a huge crowd at the rally', 'Fancy Bazaar', 'Assam', 'Guwahati', '781001', 'Speaking to huge supporters of Tarun Gogoi at Fancy Bazaar -Panbazaar area, Shri Gogoi asserted, \'People will not vote by watching TV but will vote by watching our work. The transport condition in the state was in the ICU. Now, during the last ten years and by the effort of my party now it has reached to a healthy position.\'\r\n\r\nHe further added, \' Even if we get ten seats less than earlier seventy-eight seats we will still win. I have more knowledge of lower Assam than Sarbananda and have done a lot of work in that area and I m confident that we will get more seats in lower Assam than earlier.\'\r\nVisit Gallery for more images.\r\n', NULL, 26.1831, 91.7405, '2016-04-08 19:30:00', '2016-04-08 20:30:00', '1460195356-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-09 17:05:18'),
(80, 26, 'ENG', 'CM being honoured by the people of Lumding', 'Lumding ', 'Assam', 'Nagaon', '782447', '\r\nShri Tarun Gogoi being honoured with a Jaapi as he visits Lumding of Nagaon district to meet the people and address their problems asserting that their problems would be resolved in his next term as Chief Minister of the State.\r\n\r\nShri Gogoi reminded the people of his initiatives taken during his tenure and went on to further add, \' Those who have left the party right before the polls were fair weather friends and not real friends. When I have built 15 medical colleges, five bridges over the Brahmaputra, constructed thousands of kilometers of roads, thousands of schools then how the oppositions are blaming me that I have worked only for my son\'s career.  People of Assam know who is lying.\'', NULL, 25.7516, 93.1729, '2016-04-09 11:00:00', '2016-04-09 12:00:00', '1460220232-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-09 16:43:52'),
(81, 26, 'ENG', 'Shri Tarun Gogoi on a shopping spree', 'Beltola Bazaar', 'Assam', 'Guwahati', '781028', 'With Bihu nearing, Shri Gogoi went on a shopping spree yesterday at Beltola Bazaar. He further stopped at a local tea stall and initiated a conversation with the local customers over a cup of tea. ', NULL, 26.1237, 91.8005, '2016-04-10 13:00:00', '2016-04-10 14:00:00', '1460352630-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-11 05:30:30'),
(93, 26, 'ENG', 'Assam opens its arms for the Royal couple', 'Tezpur', 'Assam', 'Tezpur', '784001', 'A grand welcome for the Duke and Duchess of Cambridge, Prince Williams, and Princess kate Middleton as they were received by our Hon\'ble Chief Minister Shri Tarun Gogoi at Tezpur airport.\r\n\r\nThe Royal couple who is on a travelling spree made its gracious presence in Assam on 12th April 2016 to witness the beauty of Assam and visit Kaziranga National park famed for one-horned rhinoceros.', NULL, 26.6331, 92.7863, '2016-04-12 18:00:00', '2016-04-14 15:36:00', '1460974087-em.jpg', 'Image', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2016-04-18 10:08:07'),
