ormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">सपने</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">आप</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">के</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">मन</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">को</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">दर्शाते</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">है।</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">मेरा</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">भी</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">एक</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">सपना</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">है</span>,\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">मैं</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">अपनी</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">मातृभूमि</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">को</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">जगद्गुरु</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">के</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">सिंहासन</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">पर</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">बैठना</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">देखना</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">चाहता</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">हू।</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">मैं</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">अपने</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">राष्ट्र</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">को</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">निडर</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">और</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">एक</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">मजबूत</span>, <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">आर्थिक</span>,\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">नैतिक</span>, <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">स्वस्थ</span>, <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">सभ्य</span>, <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">राष्ट्र</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">बनाना</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">चाहता</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">हू।</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `journeylanguagestext` (`JourneyLanguageTextID`, `journeyID`, `LanguageCode`, `biographyText`, `principleText`, `philosophyText`, `sandeshText`) VALUES
(15, 12, 'MAR', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">सदगुरु</span> <span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">श्री</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">भैय्युजी</span> <span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">महाराज</span>:\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">एक</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin\">कर्मशील</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin\">संत</span><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">परम पूज्य राष्ट्रसंत,\r\nश्री उदयसिंग देशमुख, ज्यांना भैय्यू महाराज म्हणून ओळखले जाते, ते सर्व शब्दकोशातील\r\nपरिभाषा करून संत आहेत. ते अत्यंत देखणे, सुधृद बांध्याचे, करिष्माई, उच्च शिक्षित,\r\nप्रतिभावान आणि प्रतिभाशाली गुरू वयाच्या तिशी मध्ये आहेत आणि ते \"राष्ट्रसंत\"\r\nम्हणून ओळखले जातात. ते वयाच्या पाच्या वर्षापासूनच संत म्हणून ओळखले जातात. ते अत्यंत\r\nदयाळू आणि कनवाळू आहेत आणि नेहमी विकासाची चिंता करतात. विकास आणि काळजी, शारीरिक आध्यात्मिक\r\nकिंवा अन्यथा असू शकते; पण परम पू भैय्यू महाराज सामान्य जनतेच्या अडचणी दूर करतात\r\nआणि त्यांना समाधान देण्याचा प्रयत्न करतात.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">भैय्यू</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">महाराज</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">यांचे</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">मुख्यालय</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">इंदूर</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">येथे</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">आहे</span>.\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">ते</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">प्रामुख्याने</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">महाराष्ट्रामध्ये</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">प्रकल्प</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">विकासाच्या</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">निमित्ताने</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">फिरत</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">असतात</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">आणि</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">आध्यात्मिक</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">व</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">व्यावहारिक</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">प्रवचने</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">आयोजित</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">करतात</span>. <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">त्यांचे</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">असंख्य</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">शिष्य</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">आणि</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">भक्त</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">महाराष्ट्रात</span> <span style=\"font-family: Mangal, serif;\">आहेत</span>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">पुरस्कार</span> <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">मिळाले</span>:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">१</span>. <span style=\"font-family:&quot;Mangal&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">डी</s