(114, 32, 'ENG', 'Fourth Convocation Ceremony D. Y. Patil University, Kolhapur ( Maharashtra )', 'Spiritual leader Shri Bhaiyyuji Maharaj will be conferred upon with D. Litt. degree at a fourth convocation ceremony of D. Y. Patil University, Kolhapur on April 13 this month for his exceptional services that he has been carrying for the socio-economic uplift of the poor, downtrodden, underprivileged sections of the society in Maharashtra, Madhya Pradesh, Gujarat and other parts of the country. The D. Litt. degree would be conferred upon him at the convocation ceremony by chief guest of the function Dr. K. N. Ganesh (Director, IISER, Pune). The spiritual saint Bhaiyyuji Maharaj who has his disciples across the country, through his trust – Shree Sadguru Datta Dharmik Evam Parmarthik Trust has alleviated socio-economic condition of the poor sections of the society through various projects that he has been carrying in the fields of education, agriculture, health, water conservation, environment, community development, etc.', '2016-04-12 19:52:00', '1466519070-em.Litt'),
